## Priority: High

v-model works on native form elements but is rejected on components with "not supported yet".

## Scope

- Desugar `v-model` on components to `:modelValue` + `@update:modelValue` prop/emit pair
- Support named v-model: `v-model:title='titleRef'`
- Validate against component's defineProps/defineEmits contracts

## Example

```html
<MyInput v-model='name' />
<!-- desugars to: -->
<MyInput :modelValue='name.get()' @update:modelValue='name.set' />
```